title: BRIEF-Sloneczne Inwestycje lowers stake in Fly.pl to 17.69 pct
text:
BRIEF-Sloneczne Inwestycje lowers stake in Fly.pl to 17.69 pct 
Oct 5 Fly.pl SA : 
* Said on Saturday that Sloneczne Inwestycje Sp. z o.o. on Oct. 2 reduced its stake in the company to 17.69 percent from 79.03 percent
